     C* F22: overflow. Printer OA, OFL=3. 5 detail lines; OA heading OVERFLOW prints.
     FOVDATA  IP  F      80            DISK
     FOVDOUT  O   F     132     OA     PRINTER
     LOVDOUT    5FL  3OL
     IOVDATA
     I                                        1   20N
     OOVDOUT  H  1    OA
     O                                   20 'OVERFLOW'
     OOVDOUT  D  1
     O                         N         10
